&lt;h2 id=&#34;強制切斷ssh連線&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#強制切斷ssh連線&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;強制切斷ssh連線&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;強制切斷ssh連線&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovL3NlcnZlcmZhdWx0LmNvbS9hLzI4MzEzMC8yOTMxNTg=&#34;&gt;http://serverfault.com/a/283130/293158&lt;i class=&#34;fa fa-external-link-alt&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SSH session is hanging out hoping the other side will come back&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;Enter ~ .&lt;/code&gt;: send escape sequence by the ssh client&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;Enter ~ Ctrl+Z&lt;/code&gt;: to send the ssh client to the background job queue of your local shell, then fg as normal to get it back&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;Install-without-Root-access-sudo&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Install-without-Root-access-sudo&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Install without Root access(sudo)&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Install without Root access(sudo)&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovL2Fza3VidW50dS5jb20vcXVlc3Rpb25zLzMzOS9ob3ctY2FuLWktaW5zdGFsbC1hLXBhY2thZ2Utd2l0aG91dC1yb290LWFjY2Vzcw==&#34;&gt;http://askubuntu.com/questions/339/how-can-i-install-a-package-without-root-access&lt;i class=&#34;fa fa-external-link-alt&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
